code: /**  * Return the full version string of the present Spring Boot codebase, or {@code null}  * if it cannot be determined.  * @return the version of Spring Boot or {@code null}  * @see Package#getImplementationVersion()  */ public static String getVersion() {     Package pkg = SpringBootVersion.class.getPackage().     return (pkg != null) ? pkg.getImplementationVersion() : null. }
